4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for beginners aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks with three live online classes per week, accommodating up to 16 students per class. Participants will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, networking, and server administration. The curriculum covers cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. No prior experience is needed, and the course content is available in English and Spanish. For more details, visit [the website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop